{"tid":1791491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈新準則：任何貼有建制派揮春店鋪，一律唔幫襯","createTime":"2019-12-21T01:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T04:03:28.000Z","uid":57405,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdcf9b7cc2d08cbf74cc96ffb9e5756b19b6243","tid":1791491,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:25:21.000Z","msg":"新年將至，家家戶戶都開始換月曆，貼揮春，商鋪不例外。<br />\n近幾年，各大政黨都用寫揮春、派月曆做宣傳。<br />\n但現今在黃色經濟圈大前提下，如果再有店舖掛建制派月曆同揮春，都一定唔係黃店。<br />\n我係度呼籲名位，如果發現有店舖貼有由建制派派發的月曆及揮春，請立即列出名稱，以便大家罷買罷食！"},{"pid":"fe60abb78c6dd4cda66213ffa93492c82bd7ba27","tid":1791491,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c108450e2a397f65924fb94f636b28344c8a3d7b","tid":1791491,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"啱 黃色經濟唔應該咁複雜 間間單單<br />\n唔洗查曬人哋成舖十三代係咪藍<br />\n<br />\n跟燒山方法做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d12ec3d7cab6aaf4e788bcf586f8582d3fcdcc","tid":1791491,"uid":45893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:46:22.000Z","msg":"最好列入藍店表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e35331736ccc63f089cc6a44bdad4cdc8e1f0c3","tid":1791491,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T01:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d240d167afba5f1d7a7448466105f9d7611fd366","tid":1791491,"uid":341925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"淨係貼呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSihz7S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSihz7S.jpg&h=c0014ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42ea72b20ab32b0b91913f98537c999e2ce36afd","tid":1791491,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04